text:
There is a syntax error in the /usr/local/etc/rc.d/uwsgi rc-script that makes the service interface of uwsgi unusable

Line 90:
eval uwsgi_socket_mode=\${uwsgi_${profile}_socket_mode:-${uwsgi_socket_mode}

when it should be
eval uwsgi_socket_mode=\${uwsgi_${profile}_socket_mode:-${uwsgi_socket_mode}}
